<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I dunno. How=C2=A0<em>should=C2=A0</em>people =
be doing business over text messaging? On April 17, as Musk was publicly pr=
essuring Twitter=E2=80=99s board with a semi-hostile takeover bid, the chai=
rman of the board, Bret Taylor, reached out to him by text to say =E2=80=9C=
Elon, I am just checking in to reiterate that the board is seriously review=
ing the proposal in your letter. We are working on a formal response as qui=
ckly as we can consistent with our fiduciary duties. Feel free to reach out=
