ery much Business Texting. Musk replied with the =E2=80=9Clike=E2=80=9D tap=
back. How else should he have replied? Yes, right, fiduciary duties, gotcha=
, thumbs up. He is doing big business, but he=E2=80=99s also texting. The t=
humbs-up button is right there.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">These texts make sense to me. There is a popul=
ar sense about=C2=A0Twitter that it is:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Tremendously important to society, the=
