=80=9Clol idk blockchain?=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94=C2=A0or =E2=80=9CI do not plan=
 to make money, I plan to lose money, this is a commitment to free speech,=
=E2=80=9D for that matter =E2=80=94=C2=A0then your estimate would go down. =
But:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Even if your estimate went down, it s=
