hich is trying to make money. =E2=80=9CElon Musk makes more money when he=
=E2=80=99s not trying to make money than most other people will make when t=
hey try their hardest to make money=E2=80=9D is just=C2=A0<em>obviously emp=
irically true</em>, so it is not crazy to apply it here.</li>=09<li style=
=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">If your starting estimate is high enough, and if y=
our connections to Musk are tenuous enough, is that really the text that yo=
