<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I suppose there are some people =E2=80=94 ther=
e might be one person =E2=80=94=C2=A0maybe there isn=E2=80=99t, I don=E2=80=
=99t know =E2=80=94=C2=A0whose social media consumption is mainly:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Kim Kardashian=E2=80=99s Instagram, a=
nd</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">US Securities and Exchange Comm=
ission Chair Gary Gensler=E2=80=99s YouTube channel.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Like, sure, why not. You like Kim Kardashian, =
but you also want to keep up on the latest trends in securities enforcement=
. If this is you, then last June you will have gotten Kim Kardashian=E2=80=
=99s Instagram story promoting EthereumMax, a piece of absolute crypto nons=
ense that is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29250=
431.285527/aHR0cHM6Ly9jb2lubWFya2V0Y2FwLmNvbS9jdXJyZW5jaWVzL2V0aGVyZXVtbWF4=
Lw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB0c7a0309" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"i=
temscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none =
!important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-=
bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> now trading at=C2=A0$0.00000=
0004229</a>. And then today you will have seen <a href=3D"https://link.mail=
.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29250431.285527/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueW91dHViZS5jb2=
0vd2F0Y2g_dj12YlpTNnRZUUtJTQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB3829af3f" itemprop=3D=
"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0000=
00; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bott=
om-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Ge=
nsler's YouTube video</a> that =E2=80=9Ccautions=C2=A0investors not to make=
 investment decisions based solely on the recommendations of a celebrity or=
 influencer.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=9CAh well,=E2=80=9D you will say to yourself, =
=E2=80=9Cshame I put my life savings into EthereumMax on Kim Kardashian=E2=
=80=99s recommendation, but at least now I know not to do it again.=E2=80=
=9D The system worked, for you, though with a delay that turned out to be p=
retty material. (The time to warn you not to buy crypto based on Kim Kardas=
hian=E2=80=99s touting was=C2=A0<em>before=C2=A0</em>she touted crypto.)</p=
>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But you=E2=80=99re an unusual case. Kardashian=
 has <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29250431.2855=
27/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuaW5zdGFncmFtLmNvbS9raW1rYXJkYXNoaWFuLz9obD1lbg/607f07cee=
f4b8524a319a23cBc2128896" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" ta=
rget=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; =
border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style=
: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> 331 million Instagram followers</a>. As =
of 9:30 a.m. today that Gensler video had fewer than=C2=A01,000 views. Ther=
e is a reason that she can get paid $250,000 per post to promote the purest=
 possible crypto nonsense, despite the SEC=E2=80=99s counter-programming.</=
p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness=
.com/click/29250431.285527/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9uZXdzL3ByZXNzLXJlbGVh=
c2UvMjAyMi0xODM/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB97cfb52b" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" i=
temscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-deco=
ration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00=
0000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Anyway</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Securities and Exchange Commission today a=
nnounced charges against Kim Kardashian for touting on social media a crypt=
o asset security offered and sold by EthereumMax without disclosing the pay=
ment she received for the promotion. Kardashian agreed to settle the charge=
s, pay $1.26 million in penalties, disgorgement, and interest, and cooperat=
e with the Commission=E2=80=99s ongoing investigation.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The SEC=E2=80=99s order finds that Kardashian =
failed to disclose that she was paid $250,000 to publish a post on her Inst=
agram account about EMAX tokens, the crypto asset security being offered by=
 EthereumMax. Kardashian=E2=80=99s post contained a link to the EthereumMax=
 website, which provided instructions for potential investors to purchase E=
MAX tokens.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">"This case is a reminder that, when celebritie=
s or influencers endorse investment opportunities, including crypto asset s=
ecurities, it doesn=E2=80=99t mean that those investment products are right=
 for all investors," said SEC Chair Gary Gensler. "We encourage investors t=
o consider an investment=E2=80=99s potential risks and opportunities in lig=
ht of their own financial goals."</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I would have been stronger there? I do not giv=
e investing advice around here, but a reasonable rule of thumb is =E2=80=9C=
when celebrities or influencers endorse investment opportunities, especiall=
y crypto asset securities, that definitely means that those investment prod=
ucts are wrong for all investors=E2=80=9D? Like, who <em>was=C2=A0</em>Ethe=
reumMax right for? Also, when celebrities and influencers endorse a crypto =
thing you=E2=80=99ve never heard of, it <em>definitely=C2=A0</em>means=C2=
=A0they got paid to do it? Honestly if you get an Instagram post from an in=
